quran[9{c,v,t}:
12,87,"mere bachcho, ja kar yousuf aur is ke bhai ki kuch tooh lagao, Allah ki rehmat se mayoos nah ho, is ki rehmat se to bas kafir hi mayoos howa karte hain """
12,88,"jab yeh log misar ja kar yousuf ki paishi mein daakhil hue to unhon ne arz kya ke"" ae sardar ba Iqtidaar , hum aur hamaray ahal o Ayal sakht museebat mein mubtala hain aur hum kuch haqeer si poonji le kar aeye hain, aap hamein bhar poor ghalla inayat farmaen aur hum ko khairaat den, Allah khairaat karne walon ko jaza deta hai """
12,89,"( yeh sun کریوسف se nah raha gaya ) uss ne kaha"" tumhe kuch yeh bhi maloom hai ke tum ne yousuf aur uss ke bhai ke sath kya kya tha jabkay tum nadaan thay """
12,90,"woh choank kar bolay"" kya tum yousuf ho ?"" uss ne kaha,"" haan, mein yousuf hon aur yeh mera bhai hai Allah ne hum par ahsaan farmaya haqeeqat yeh hai ke agar koi taqwa aur sabr se kaam le to Allah ke haan aisay naik logon ka ajar mara nahi jata """
12,91,"unhon ne kaha"" ba khuda ke tum ko Allah ne hum par fazeelat bakhsh aur waqai hum khata car thay """
12,92,"is ne jawab diya,"" aaj tum par koi girift nahi, Allah tumhe maaf kere, woh sab se barh kar reham frmane wala hai"
12,93,"jao, mera yeh kameez le jao aur mere waalid ke mun par daal do, unn ki benaye palat aeye gi, aur apne sab ahal o Ayal ko mere paas le aao """
12,94,"jab yeh qaafla ( misar se ) rawana howa to un ke baap ne ( canaan mein ) kaha"" mein yousuf ki khusbhoo mehsoos kar raha hon, tum log kahin yeh nah kehnay lagu ke mein burhapay mein sathya gaya hon """
12,95,"ghar ke log bolay"" khuda ki qasam aap abhi taq apne isi puranay khabt mein parre hue hain """
